Slot machines are located in the Golden Treasure Casino.  You must be
sitting at the slot machine to begin play.

Syntax: play slots <number>

The number parameter is a digit from 1-5 indicating both the amount
that you will bet as well as the amount you will receive if the slot
machine hits.

Slot machines will take money from your on-hand cash automatically.  If
you win at the slot machine, the winnings are in the slot machine's
tray, so be sure to GET TALENS SLOT before leaving.

